subSubSection.paragraph:
Holotype
♂
: tegulum pear-shaped, apically narrow and wider at base (
Fig. 1c
). Embolus short, slightly thorn-like (
Fig. 1c
). Palpal tibia with small apophysis on retrolateral margin (
Fig. 1d
). Palpal femur with serrated retrolateral margin and with very small ventral distal apophysis (
Fig. 1c
—dva). Carapace 0.950 long, 0.530 wide in cephalic area, 0.780 wide in thoracic area. Abdomen 0.880 long, 0.760 wide. Palpal femur 0.187, tibia 0.127, patella 0.148, cymbium 0.363. Abdomen covered by dorsal scutum, ventral sclerite subtriangular, broader than long (
Fig. 1a, b
). Eye sizes and interdistances: AME 0.047, ALE 0.048, PME 0.080, PLE 0.068; AME–AME 0.043, AME–ALE 0.038, ALE–PLE 0.043, PME–PME 0.055, PME–PLE 0.042. MOQ 0.180 wide.
